tag name|||Synth Riders: GoST - "Behemoth (Perturbator Remix)"
tag jj|||Synth Riders goes “Back to the Synths” to celebrate 5 years of riding the rails with the “Synthwave Essentials Volume 3” music pack! Headlined by The Midnight, this 10 song pack (5 free songs, 5 paid DLC) also features a brand new cover of New Order’s classic “Blue Monday”, created just for Synth Riders by legendary DJ Zardonic! Also in the pack are tracks and remixes featuring Starcadian, GoST, Ollie Wride, Dance With The Dead, Scandroid, LeBrock and PRIZM. Enjoy these great tracks in “Back to the Synths”, one of our original play Stages which has received a special “glow-up” to coincide with our birthday!  Add “Behemoth” (Perturbator Remix) by GosT to your library!  Take an epic track from “underground master of slasherwave” GoST, invite the “new king of synthesized horror and sci-fi” Perturbator to remix and you get music straight out of an 80s horror movie, best enjoyed loudly at midnight!
